title: Four Big Questions About 'Bling Empire'
description:
Juliet Litman and Amelia Wedemeyer try to understand 'Bling Empire,' a Netflix reality TV show that follows a group of extremely rich Asian people living in Los Angeles.

Hosts: Juliet Litman and Amelia Wedemeyer
